      "title": "Immitation Learning in Isaacsim",
      "content": "Take-away from https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eO5wMzw9LeQ&t=6s\n\n- The data downloaded as part of the custom policy training examples are stored\n  /home/mbwh_0/.cache/huggingface/lerobot/lerobot\\\n- Any dataset we prepare, the primary objective is to make it follow the Lerobot standard format\n  - /data/tvp_ws/rlearning_ws/lerobot/src/lerobot/datasets/lerobot_dataset.py - Follow this to know what is the standard format expected for Lerobot",
