      "id": "8tltt970",
      "title": "RMPFLOW Setup for a UR5E + Robotiq85",
      "content": "For RMPFlow establishment, 3 files are required:\n1. A URDF file of the custom robot for specifying the robot kinematics.\n2. A supplementary robot description file in YAML format - this file is generated using the Lula Robot Description Editor UI tool\n3. An RMPflow configuration file in the YAML format, containing the parameters for all the enabled RMPs\n\n\n**Robot Description File**\n- ",
