      "id": "8zz7nj2n",
      "title": "2025-08-24 — Daily",
      "content": "# Top 3\n- [ ] \n- [ ] \n- [ ] \n\n## Tasks\n\n## Journal\n### <u>Tedx</u>\n<u>3 lessons on starting over</u>\n- Be curious - \n> \"Be curious, not judgmental\"\n- Believe that you can learn - Have the growth mindset - Learn to appreciate enthusiasm and hard work over talent\n- Take home wherever you go\n\n### <u>Thinkschool</u>\n- In China, your economic performance as a leader works more like your resume\n- It's never enough to know the bare minimum\n- Ghost cities - Vicious cycle: More Constructions -> Higher GDP Figures -> Better Career for local officials\n- Debt Swap Program \n\n<u> **Important Lessons** </u>\n- Growth without Demand is a Mirage - Infrastructure must follow real needs and not just targets\n- Transparency is not optional, but a protection\n- Incentives can drive the system for the better or worse.\n\n\n\n\n## Wins\n",
