      "id": "k2w7tuqq",
      "title": "2025-08-30 — Daily",
      "content": "# Top 3\n- [ ] \n- [ ] \n- [ ] \n\n## Tasks\n### VC Playbook - Nikhil Kammat Podcast\n- Emerging AI Trends\n  - Engineering is becoming more valuable\n  - Data to be crucial for training AI models\n  - China to continue leading the AI market\n  - AI Usage in medical and legal services\n  - Agentic AI to work for a longer duration\n  - AGI to emerge as a gradual drift\n  - Building datasets to train AI on physical world\n\n- Tangential effect of AI on humankind:\n  - Decrease in birth rate as people are relying on devices and social media to meet their emotional needs\n  - Potentially, humans as a species might get sidelined like pets. They will be loved and fed and taken care of by AI.\n  - A lot of important decisions that run the world would be taken by AI.\n  - It is also important who the creators of these AIs are,  as if the makers are all of the same cloth, the AI made by them might not represent all the voices.\n  - AI Religion\n  - Universal Basic Income(UBI) \n  - Matchmaking would change\n \n- Interesting Ideas\n  - Off-grid products will do better. \n  - Outcome-focused Education\n  - Secondary markets for private companies would become mainstream\n  - The world would be older and sicker, hence longevity, wellness, and health would become big\n  - Senior Living welfare as a community. \n  - Too much attention on attention \n \n## Journal\n\n## Wins\n",
