      "id": "vrfg5ie8",
      "title": "Robot Assembly using Robot Assembler",
      "content": "## Robot Assembly in Isaac Sim using Robot Assembler\n\n### Approach 1: Via URDF Importer\n- Custom Arm Urdf + Gripper Urdf - worked\n- Custom Arm Urdf + Isaac Sim Gripper - Worked\n***Note: All the UR usds were not getting recognized in the assembler***\n\n\n",
