    {
      "id": "zhjzkrmo",
      "title": "UR5E+Robotiq2F85 Moveit Setup Assistant",
      "content": "ros2_control URDF Modifications with all Command Interfaces and State Interfaces enabled - Position, Velocity & Effort\n```yaml  \n                     <joint name=\"shoulder_pan_joint\">\n                <command_interface name=\"position\"/>\n                <command_interface name=\"velocity\"/>\n                <command_interface name=\"effort\"/>\n                <state_interface name=\"position\">\n                  <param name=\"initial_value\">${initial_positions['shoulder_pan_joint']}</param>\n                </state_interface>\n                <state_interface name=\"velocity\"/>\n                <state_interface name=\"effort\"/>\n            </joint>\n            <joint name=\"shoulder_lift_joint\">\n                <command_interface name=\"position\"/>\n                <command_interface name=\"velocity\"/>\n                <command_interface name=\"effort\"/>\n                <state_interface name=\"position\">\n                  <param name=\"initial_value\">${initial_positions['shoulder_lift_joint']}</param>\n                </state_interface>\n                <state_interface name=\"velocity\"/>\n                <state_interface name=\"effort\"/>\n            </joint>\n            <joint name=\"elbow_joint\">\n                <command_interface name=\"position\"/>\n                <command_interface name=\"velocity\"/>\n                <command_interface name=\"effort\"/>\n                <state_interface name=\"position\">\n                  <param name=\"initial_value\">${initial_positions['elbow_joint']}</param>\n                </state_interface>\n                <state_interface name=\"velocity\"/>\n                <state_interface name=\"effort\"/>\n            </joint>\n            <joint name=\"wrist_1_joint\">\n                <command_interface name=\"position\"/>\n                <command_interface name=\"velocity\"/>\n                <command_interface name=\"effort\"/>\n                <state_interface name=\"position\">\n                  <param name=\"initial_value\">${initial_positions['wrist_1_joint']}</param>\n                </state_interface>\n                <state_interface name=\"velocity\"/>\n                <state_interface name=\"effort\"/>\n            </joint>\n            <joint name=\"wrist_2_joint\">\n                <command_interface name=\"position\"/>\n                <command_interface name=\"velocity\"/>\n                <command_interface name=\"effort\"/>\n                <state_interface name=\"position\">\n                  <param name=\"initial_value\">${initial_positions['wrist_2_joint']}</param>\n                </state_interface>\n                <state_interface name=\"velocity\"/>\n                <state_interface name=\"effort\"/>\n            </joint>\n            <joint name=\"wrist_3_joint\">\n                <command_interface name=\"position\"/>\n                <command_interface name=\"velocity\"/>\n                <command_interface name=\"effort\"/>\n                <state_interface name=\"position\">\n                  <param name=\"initial_value\">${initial_positions['wrist_3_joint']}</param>\n                </state_interface>\n                <state_interface name=\"velocity\"/>\n                <state_interface name=\"effort\"/>\n            </joint>\n            <joint name=\"robotiq_85_left_knuckle_joint\">\n                <command_interface name=\"position\"/>\n                <command_interface name=\"velocity\"/>\n                <command_interface name=\"effort\"/>\n                <state_interface name=\"position\">\n                  <param name=\"initial_value\">${initial_positions['robotiq_85_left_knuckle_joint']}</param>\n                </state_interface>\n                <state_interface name=\"velocity\"/>\n                <state_interface name=\"effort\"/>\n            </joint>\n\n```\n\nros2_control URDF Modifications with Position Command Interfaces and Position & Velocity State Interfaces enabled\n\n```yaml\n            <joint name=\"shoulder_pan_joint\">\n                <command_interface name=\"position\"/>\n                <state_interface name=\"position\">\n                  <param name=\"initial_value\">${initial_positions['shoulder_pan_joint']}</param>\n                </state_interface>\n                <state_interface name=\"velocity\"/>\n            </joint>\n            <joint name=\"shoulder_lift_joint\">\n                <command_interface name=\"position\"/>\n                <state_interface name=\"position\">\n                  <param name=\"initial_value\">${initial_positions['shoulder_lift_joint']}</param>\n                </state_interface>\n                <state_interface name=\"velocity\"/>\n            </joint>\n            <joint name=\"elbow_joint\">\n                <command_interface name=\"position\"/>\n                <state_interface name=\"position\">\n                  <param name=\"initial_value\">${initial_positions['elbow_joint']}</param>\n                </state_interface>\n                <state_interface name=\"velocity\"/>\n            </joint>\n            <joint name=\"wrist_1_joint\">\n                <command_interface name=\"position\"/>\n                <state_interface name=\"position\">\n                  <param name=\"initial_value\">${initial_positions['wrist_1_joint']}</param>\n                </state_interface>\n                <state_interface name=\"velocity\"/>\n            </joint>\n            <joint name=\"wrist_2_joint\">\n                <command_interface name=\"position\"/>\n                <state_interface name=\"position\">\n                  <param name=\"initial_value\">${initial_positions['wrist_2_joint']}</param>\n                </state_interface>\n                <state_interface name=\"velocity\"/>\n            </joint>\n            <joint name=\"wrist_3_joint\">\n                <command_interface name=\"position\"/>\n                <state_interface name=\"position\">\n                  <param name=\"initial_value\">${initial_positions['wrist_3_joint']}</param>\n                </state_interface>\n                <state_interface name=\"velocity\"/>\n            </joint>\n```\n",
