      "id": "wl0lav4j",
      "title": "2025-11-05 — Daily",
      "content": "# Top 3\n- Fix ROS2BAG to Lerobot Policy Training Pipeline\n- Complete all travel related formalities\n- Clean all the PHD related tasks\n\n## Tasks\n- ROS2BAG To Lerobot\n  - Understand, finalize and fix the time sync issue between topics from sim and outside sim\n    - Understand what is the difference in going with 'header' or 'recieve'\n    - Understand if enabling something within the simulation or having a ros clock node could solve the issue\n      - Basically understand what is the right way to do time sync in these scenarios\n  - Re-record a rosbag with the fix. Generate tests to ensure it doesn't violate any time sync related rules\n  - Test converting to Lerobot pipeline \n    - Ensure all the data required for lerobot training is decoded as expected. If not fix what is broken\n- ADC\n  - Integrate the data collection services to the ADC BT\n  - PnP Fixed Poses  - Randomize with white to colored regions idea - keep a number i.e if 100 samples were successful stop\n  \n\n## Journal\n\n## Wins\n",
