      "id": "iropwf6c",
      "title": "2025-11-17 — Daily",
      "content": "# Top 3\n- [ ] \n- [ ] \n- [ ] \n\n## Tasks\nMain Quest:\n  1. Fix the Time Misalignment issue with Robot Learning compatible Motion Planner Stack\n    - Ensure that the lead time between action command and the joint states is mostly predictive, slightly aligned, and hardly ever reactive\n      - Test it out for multiple sequences and confirm that there are no abnormal behaviours\n    - Confirm if the Camera Frame sync issue is real. If yes, fix it\n      - Verify if the behaviour is happening due to wrongly timed BT calls\n        - Replay rosbags at random and qualitatively confirm if there is a sync issue in the calls\n      - Verify if the behaviour is due to an error in the bag2lerobot conversion script\n        - Check if it is fundamentally a problem with the conversion script itself\n        - Or happening only while processing multiple bags at the same time\n\n  2. Record all the leanings in a doc\n\n\n## Journal\n\n## Wins\n",
