      "mood": "😐",
      "journal": "I started out great today. Worked out after a long time.\n\nHad a quick call with Sree in the morning. We thought of talking with Manichechi and Vipinattan but for some reason that didn't happen.\n\nSomething wasn't alright between us. I don't know what exactly it was that bothered me. Probably the fact that I lose in her often in between our conversations. I wish she handled this side with more warmth. It could be me not having a mature take on this.\n\nI couldn't complete a lot of tasks I wished to comple today. Did a complete bug fix of the note app so that from tomorrow onwards I'm more disciplined and consistent which I'll be as well.\n\nShe was a chakara and tried to patch things up but typical me couldn't get over it. I love her and I would make up for it.\n\nI'm not losing this race. I'm coming back stronger. I know I was never the most talented but I always made it because I could always and always bet on my ability to work hard to compensate for the talent I missed. So the plan is the same to just be consistent and be at it. Small step by step!\n\n",
      "deletedAt": null
