      "id": "9ajyl0ju",
      "title": "2026-02-18 — Daily",
      "content": "# Top 3\n- Fully understand the VR Teleoperation Code\n  - COntroller WOrking\n  - COncept of Rotation\n  - IK\n- Integrate the Gripper\n- [ ] \n- [ ] \n\n\nHow to break a bad habit?\n- Studies say no matter how hard we try to focus, some would still drift into daydream\n- Trigger - Behaviour - Reward\n- The prefrontal cortex tends to always motivate us to do the right thing\n  - For the note, it is the first part of the brain that goes offline when we are stressed\n- Be mindful of the action to embed deeply what it does to you \n    - Notice the urge, get curious, enjoy letting it go\n\n## Tasks\n\n## Journal\n\n## Wins\n",
