      "id": "sddej8ha",
      "title": "Superyou Casestudy",
      "content": "- Better for you category is rising in India\n- Its never been hard to start a brand and never been harder to sustain a brand\n- Demand for new products ever so high - especially for 7-8% india\n- Health and Better for you  - most marketted space\n- Supposedly the new generation dont want to eat the exact same thing the old generation ate\n    - there should be excitement around the product\n- Damage control in the food space\n- Throw one punch but make that count!\n- The impressions from a reel or social media content by iteself doesnt mean anything unless what it intended to do stayed with the consumers\n- Price of a product sets the expectation for the product  \n- Brands has to optimize on the values it want to sell their products based on to their consumer\n- A brand cant be everything for everyone\n- In simple Brand building is about standing for something\n- **Seth Godin said that if same two items are kept on the table, the extra you pay for A compared to B is the brand value of A**\n",
      "tags": [
        "thinkschoo",
        "business",
        "startup"
      ],
      "projectId": null,
      "dateIndex": null,
      "type": "note",
      "pinned": false,
      "createdAt": "2026-02-26T03:38:49.075Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-02-27T03:13:57.277Z",
      "attachments": [],
      "links": []
