      "id": "d8gtp9rq",
      "title": "Money Rules ",
      "content": "What are the 3 ways to make money?\n- Structure, Momentum and Asymmetry\nThe role of each:\n  - Momentum - How to compound money more\n  - Structure - Who controls money and what outcomes you get\n  - Asymmetry - Maximize the upside and minimize the downside\n\n7 laws:\n  - Money loves speed but wealth loves time - Make a good decision and hold on to it for a long period of time instead of running behind opportunities and acting on them\n  - He who gives the money has the power - 3 kind of poeple \n    - People who build wealth from their income\n    - Poeple who build from selling an entity\n    - People who build from Buying and Building\n  - Leverage multiples everything\n  - Cashflow makes you alive and equity makes you free\n  - Risk and Reward are non-linear \n  - You dont risk the empire for a pot of gold - Learn to size bets\n  - Diversify is a hedge against ignorance\n    ",
      "tags": [],
      "projectId": "y9081w3r",
      "dateIndex": null,
      "type": "note",
      "pinned": false,
