      "id": "d5gwjojn",
      "title": "Automated Data Collection Pipeline - Policy Inference Instructions",
      "content": "`Terminal 1:\ncd /data/tvp_ws/rlearning_ws\nsource /opt/ros/humble/setup.bash\nsource /data/tvp_ws/ros/ros2/tvp_auto_data_collection_ws/install/setup.bash\nsource install/setup.bash\n\nros2 launch rosetta ur5e_policy_bridge.launch.py or\nros2 launch rosetta ur5e_policy_bridge.launch.py \\\n    actions_per_chunk:=50 \\\n    ema_alpha:=1.0 \\\n    chunk_size_threshold:=0.3\n\n\nTerminal 2:\nsource /opt/ros/humble/setup.bash\nsource /data/tvp_ws/ros/ros2/tvp_auto_data_collection_ws/install/setup.bash\nsource install/setup.bash\n\nsource /opt/ros/humble/setup.bash && source /data/tvp_ws/ros/ros2/tvp_auto_data_collection_ws/install/setup.bash && source /data/tvp_ws/rlearning_ws/install/setup.bash && ros2 action send_goal /run_policy rosetta_interfaces/action/RunPolicy \"{prompt: 'pick and place'}\" --feedback\n\n\nTo stop:\nros2 action send_goal /run_policy rosetta_interfaces/action/RunPolicy \"{}\" --cancel`",
