      "content": "# Top 3\n- Complete ACT lecture\n- Scan documents for Pappa\n- Bring the leros2 to a state where all that is left for tomorrow is collecting data\n- Look for and start the procedures for Visa Slot Appointment\n\n## Tasks\n\n## Journal\n\n## Wins\n\n\n## Andrey Karpathy: From Vibe Coding to AI Agent\n- Intresting Thoughts:\n  - Clasiical Computing was all about building systems like Calculators\n  - Modern daya NNs live in a virtual world build like calculators\n  - The natural progression would be to build computers which are basically Neural Network itself\n\n - Concept of Varifiability:\n  - The models capabilites are at the mercy of what the labs put into the pretraining data distribution mix\n    - Hence there is no manual and you dont what the model could actually do and can not do\n    - Agentic Engineering vs Vibe Coding\n    - You can outsource your thinking but you cant outsource your understanding",
