      "id": "off677tk",
      "title": "How to Build a Self-Improving Company with AI",
      "content": "- Most companies today are organized like Roman Legion where humans are the conduit for information flowing up and down\n- There is even a famous quote by Jack Dorsey that \"There is always an underlying assumption that organizations have to be hierarchically organized with humans as the coordination mechanism\n\n- AI should not be just about productivity but about capability\n\n- A typical AI loop:\n   - Sensors/Data\n   - Policy Layer\n   - Tool Layer\n   - Quality Gates\n   - Learning mechanism",
