      "id": "osewwann",
      "title": "🗺️ Topic Map — Autonomy",
      "content": "# 🗺️ Topic Map — Autonomy\n\n> Living map of what's happening in this area. Update during the weekly triage. The point of this note is that **in 60 seconds you can sound informed about Autonomy** to a PI, an interviewer, or a collaborator.\n\n## 🧑‍🔬 Key people & labs\n- (Name — affiliation — what they're known for — 1 representative paper)\n\n## 📜 Seminal works (must-cite foundations)\n- (Author, Year — title — why it matters)\n\n## 🆕 Recent (last 6 months)\n- (Author, Year — title — 1-line so-what)\n\n## ❓ Open problems\n- (What's still hard / unsolved / contested)\n\n## 🎯 My angle / what I'd contribute\n- (Where my background gives me leverage; what gap I'd attack)\n\n## 🔗 Related paper notes\n- [[ ]]\n",
