Robot-Autonomy-2628-CD/1362409457/\n- [ ] [2026-06-02 17:07] Paper page - MolmoAct2: Action Reasoning Models for Real-world Deployment — https://huggingface.co/papers/2605.02881\n- [ ] [2026-06-02 17:03] — https://arxiv.org/pdf/2603.26997\n- [ ] [2026-06-02 16:47] https://arxiv.org/pdf/2511.09497\n- [ ] [2026-06-01 15:01] 🗺️ World Models · GitHub - galilai-group/stable-worldmodel: A platform for reproducible world model research and evaluation · GitHub — https://github.com/galilai-group/stable-worldmodel\n- [ ] [2026-06-01 06:41] 🗺️ World Models · [2510.16732] A Comprehensive Survey on World Models for Embodied AI — https://arxiv.org/abs/2510.16732\n- [ ] [2026-06-01 06:07] [2605.08450] Zero-shot Imitation Learning by Latent Topology Mapping — https://arxiv.org/abs/2605.08450\n- [ ] [2026-06-01 05:09] — https://openaccess.thecvf.com/content/CVPR2026F/papers/Jiang_IRL-VLA_Vision-Language-Action_Training_via_Reward_World_Model_CVPRF_2026_paper.pdf\n<!--trashed:2026-06-24T04:28:31.690Z--> - [ ] [2026-06-01 03:50] https://zhaohengyin.github.io/dexteritygen/\n",
