      "content": "# Top 3\n- [ ] \n- [ ] \n- [ ] \n\n## Tasks\n\n## Journal\n\n## Wins\n\n## How the Anthropic's Genius Move Made It Legendary!\n- Scaling Laws:\n    -  In any domain, when a sufficiently capable model is fed with more data, it exponentially gets better\n\n> Great entreupreneur is defined by the most non-obvious insight they have about an industry that no one else believes in.\n\n- Anthropic is built as a Public Benefit Corporation\n    - The legal duty is not about making more money but to optimize for public benefit. They took it one step forward by investingin the idea of Long Term Benefit Trust - The trustees in this trust owns no financial stake and their sole objective is to ensure public safety and welfare\n\n- To eliminate the problem of having human bias in the response given by an AI anthropic built someting called an constitutional AI unlike an army of humans its an army of ai agents that ground all the responses based on a set of written constitutional values or rules and grades responsed based on it \n    - Step 1: The AI answers and put itself on trials - Basically it reads its answers and evaluates the responses against the rules and values in the constitution\n    - Step 2: Rewrites the answers by arguing with itself until it aligns with the rules\n    - Step 3: The AI becomes its own rater by picking up the answer that best aligns with the rules - RL from Agent Feedback\n\n",
