    {
      "id": "9rbe0iru",
      "title": "Imitation Learning in Isaccsim using Lerobot + ROS2",
      "status": "DONE",
      "due": null,
      "noteId": "7eigs8og",
      "projectId": "c7szb5bi",
      "priority": "high",
      "description": "The idea is to teach a robot a task from demonstrations performed in IsaacSim using the Lerobot framework in ROS2\n\nCurrent Running Pipeline:\nTerminal 1:\nmbwh_0@tvpian-hub:/data/tvp_ws/rlearning_ws$ ros2 launch dummy_modalities_cpp multimodal.launch.py \n\nTerminal 2:\n\n\n\nTerminal 3:\npython /data/tvp_ws/rlearning_ws/src/teleop_collect/teleop_collect/convert_to_lerobot.py   --mcap     /data/tvp_ws/rlearning_ws/data/teleop/accepted/episode_20250916_001829_070764_2fef   --resample /data/tvp_ws/rlearning_ws/src/teleop_collect/cfg/yaml/resample.yaml   --export   /data/tvp_ws/rlearning_ws/src/teleop_collect/cfg/yaml/export.yaml   --out      out/lerobot_dataset/ep1   --episode-index 0\n\n\n\n\nSecond Running Pipeline for Lerobot V2.1:\nTerminal 1:\nrsac45\n\nTerminal 2:\nros2 launch dummy_modalities_cpp multimodal.launch.py - Adjust the publisher_config.yaml to mock publish only robot and teleop joint state values\n\nTerminal 3:\n(/data/conda_envs/tvp_ilab_py310) mbwh_0@tvpian-hub:/data/tvp_ws/rlearning_ws$ python /data/tvp_ws/rlearning_ws/src/teleop_collect/teleop_collect/episode_recorder_node_v3.py   --config /data/tvp_ws/rlearning_ws/src/teleop_collect/cfg/yaml/topics_v3.yaml --threads 8\n\n\nTerminal 4:\nFor converting to Lerobot V2.1 format in batch\npython run_batch_v21.py   --episodes-root /data/tvp_ws/rlearning_ws/data/teleop/accepted   --out datasets/my_robot_v21   --resample-yaml resample_v21.yaml   --start-idx 0   --use-teleop-as-action\n\n\n",
      "subtasks": [
        {
          "id": "1ydavip0",
          "title": "Establish a dummy publisher to simuate Hardwares and Robots in the setup",
          "status": "DONE"
        },
        {
          "id": "alc5khzy",
          "title": "Data Collector - Decide and implement a script to collect the raw data in untampered form",
          "status": "DONE"
        },
        {
          "id": "0eyl0135",
          "title": "Data Collector - Create a quality evaluation pipeline of the raw data",
          "status": "DONE"
        },
        {
          "id": "8b720ra3",
          "title": "Data Sampler - Read raw data and resample to create a complete table",
          "status": "DONE"
        },
        {
          "id": "3j2id7ux",
          "title": "Data Sampler - Evaluate the quality of the resampled data",
          "status": "DONE"
        },
        {
          "id": "3gm5768i",
          "title": "Data Porter - Read the resampled data and port it to Lerobot Dataset format",
          "status": "DONE"
        },
        {
          "id": "fh75rdqz",
          "title": "Test the Data Collector on Isaacsim and Establish replay feature",
          "status": "DONE"
        },
        {
