      "tags": [],
      "description": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "tpl5",
      "name": "Research Summary",
      "content": "# Research Summary: [Topic]\n\n## Objective\n\n## Key Findings\n- \n\n## Implications\n\n## Next Steps\n",
      "updatedAt": "2026-02-22T21:03:49.720Z",
      "tags": [],
      "description": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "tpl6",
      "name": "Course / Lecture Notes",
      "content": "# Course / Lecture: [Title]\n**Course:** [Course]\n**Module / Week:** \n**Date:** [Date]\n**Instructor:** \n\n## Session Overview\nBrief summary...\n\n## Key Concepts\n- Term: Definition\n- \n\n## Detailed Notes\n- \n\n## Examples / Demonstrations\n- \n\n## Important Formulas / Patterns\n```\n\n```\n\n## Questions / Clarifications Needed\n- [ ] \n\n## Action Items / Practice\n- [ ] \n\n## References\n- \n\n## Summary (1–2 sentences)\n\n",
      "updatedAt": "2026-02-22T21:03:49.720Z",
      "tags": [],
      "description": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "tpl7",
      "name": "Project Execution Log",
      "content": "# Project Execution Log: [Project Name]\n**Date:** [Date]\n**Phase / Sprint:** \n\n## Context\nCurrent objective / scope.\n\n## Goals for This Session\n- [ ] \n\n## Procedure / Steps Performed\n1. \n2. \n\n## Commands / Tools Used\n```\n# command snippets\n```\n\n## Issues Encountered\n| Issue | Impact | Resolution |\n|-------|--------|------------|\n|  |  |  |\n\n## Decisions Made\n- Decision: Rationale\n\n## Metrics / Measurements\n- \n\n## Observations / Insights\n- \n\n## Risks / Blockers\n- \n\n## Artifacts / Outputs\n- \n\n## Next Actions\n- [ ] \n\n## Retrospective (What went well / improve)\n- Went well: \n- Improve: \n\n",
      "updatedAt": "2026-02-22T21:03:49.720Z",
      "tags": [],
      "description": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "x30bcmw7",
      "name": "Daily Task Tracker",
      "content": "# Daily Task Tracker — {{DATE}}\n\n## Morning Focus\n- [ ] Review yesterday’s progress\n- [ ] Set top 3 priorities for the day\n- [ ] System or environment checks\n- [ ] Team sync or stand-up summary\n\n---\n\n## Core Tasks\n\n### Task 1: (e.g., Auto Data Collection Pipeline)\n- [ ] Define objective\n- [ ] Subtask 1\n- [ ] Subtask 2\n- [ ] Subtask 3\n- [ ] Completion summary\n\n### Task 2: (e.g., MoveIt–IsaacSim Alignment)\n- [ ] Define objective\n- [ ] Subtask 1\n- [ ] Subtask 2\n- [ ] Subtask 3\n- [ ] Completion summary\n\n---\n\n## Experiments / Testing\n- [ ] Hypothesis\n- [ ] Setup\n- [ ] Observation log\n- [ ] Results summary\n- [ ] Outcome verified\n\n---\n\n## Debug / Fixes\n- [ ] Issue 1  \n  - [ ] Root cause  \n  - [ ] Fix  \n  - [ ] Validation  \n- [ ] Issue 2  \n  - [ ] Root cause  \n  - [ ] Fix  \n  - [ ] Validation  \n\n---\n\n## Learnings & Notes\n- Key insight 1  \n- Key insight 2  \n- Things to try next time  \n- [ ] Add to documentation or repository notes\n\n---\n\n## End-of-Day Review\n- [ ] Summary of progress\n- [ ] Blockers or pending items\n- [ ] Plan for tomorrow\n- [ ] Log metrics or performance summary",
      "createdAt": "2025-11-05T17:39:04.664Z",
      "updatedAt": "2025-11-05T17:39:04.664Z",
      "tags": [],
      "description": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "tpl_paper",
      "name": "Research Paper",
      "content": "# [Year] [Author] — [Short Title]\n\n**Citation:** \n**Link / DOI:** \n**Venue:** \n**Read on:** [Date]\n**Tags:** #\n\n## Why I read it\n\n## TL;DR (1 sentence)\n\n## Key ideas\n- \n- \n- \n\n## Method (1 paragraph)\n\n## Results that matter\n- \n\n## Limitations / pushback\n- \n\n## ✨ Inspirations for my work\n- \n\n## Open questions\n- \n\n## Related work to chase\n- \n",
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-14T01:37:08.073Z",
      "tags": [],
      "description": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "tpl_paper_note",
      "name": "Paper Note",
      "description": "Structured reading note — TL;DR, method, why-I-care, links to topic maps.",
      "tags": [
        "research",
        "paper"
      ],
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-04T15:28:39.828Z",
      "content": "# [Title]\n\n**Authors:** \n**Venue / Year:** \n**Link:** \n**Date read:** 2026-06-04\n\n## TL;DR (≤3 sentences)\n- \n\n## Problem & motivation\n- \n\n## Method (in my own words)\n- \n\n## Key results\n- \n\n## Why I care / how it connects to my work\n- \n\n## Limitations / open questions\n- \n\n## Connects to\n- [[🗺️ Topic Map — ]]\n\n## Follow-ups\n- [ ] \n"
    },
    {
      "id": "tpl_person",
      "name": "Person",
      "description": "Researcher dossier — who they are, what they work on, who they know.",
      "tags": [
        "person"
      ],
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-05T18:22:28.209Z",
      "content": "# [Name]\n\n**Role:** Prof / Postdoc / PhD / Research Engineer / Founder / …\n**Affiliation:** Lab or Team @ Org\n**Location:** \n**Tags:** \n**Met:** no\n**Star:** no\n\n## Currently working on\n- \n\n## Lab / team\n- Lab page: \n- Advisor / mentor: \n- Advisees / reports: \n- Frequent collaborators: \n- Team's main focus: \n\n## Key papers / projects\n- \n\n## Topics\n- \n\n## Online\n- Scholar: \n- GitHub: \n- Site: \n- X / Twitter: \n- LinkedIn: \n\n## How I first encountered them\n- \n\n## Insights & memorable quotes\n- \n\n## Open questions I'd want to ask\n- \n\n## Notes / threads\n- \n"
    }
